## Closeout Protocol

Before ending meaningful work, close out in the user's language with: what changed or was checked, what verification ran and the actual result, what remains/failed/is blocked, and the recommended next step. For phase-based work, include numeric done/remaining percentages. If localhost, VPS, or production status matters, report the exact check result and do not imply it works unless it responded.

